    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This driver-spec example features a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The vehicle has undergone proactive maintenance including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe. The suspension geometry remains precise with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed polyurethane bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and a linear torque curve. A well-sorted chassis for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
