      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for all my trips around town. It drives like a dream and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today! If you're looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and well-kept, this is the one for you. Feel free to shoot me a message\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
