    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS for exceptional throttle response. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring a visceral, driver-centric experience. The chassis has been maintained with precision, including documented rear subframe reinforcement and recent rod bearing prophylaxis to ensure long-term reliability. Suspension kinematics remain sharp, providing the balanced handling and high-speed stability this platform is renowned for. This is a well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the purist who values mechanical integrity and a linear 8,000 RPM powerband.",
